{"tid":1335192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[P牌破處]關於721我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-07-20T11:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T11:47:35.000Z","uid":281096,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"22cfc48a0485c677a2c1ecf617d674a68737c06a","tid":1335192,"uid":281096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"香城Online新副本在即，<br />\n相信呢刻咁多位手足個心燒到好紅，<br />\n老實講我都係。<br />\n<br />\n不過無論你諗住玩咩職，<br />\n我都希望大家記得留命。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為比起DPS有幾多，<br />\n坦得住啲咩先係重點。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">尤其尤其尤其</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">切勿狂戰士化！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記得每一次用力量，<br />\n都背負住自己嘅理念同目的，<br />\n呢個就係我地同啲怪嘅分別。<br />\n<br />\n輸出固然係爽快，<br />\n但係成功推完個副本先係重點。<br />\n我知道你地會明白。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得保護好自己，<br />\n留命就可以成大事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/44441\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F44441&h=8fc0e139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721 我地夢中相會</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/20/2He4pc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F20%2F2He4pc.jpeg&h=6c0fb96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56f56e3b40be6894dd99e081130a85bdf2acd65","tid":1335192,"uid":281096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"64cf196ae62dd99f9c